data.description: Are you over the shoebox cookie cutter street you drive down everyday? Me too. Take a stroll down Windsor Drive and escape that life. Mature trees and unique houses everywhere you look. The coolest of them all is this one with a brick paver'ed entry way, mid century modern updates in the open concept common areas and ton of natural light and exposed brick. Its everything you want for entertaining or relaxing with your family. Features two bedrooms upstairs and two bedrooms downstairs.
